Name: Ultimate Disc Golf
About the game: Disc Golf is a fun and easy to pick up sport that involves taking a disc and throwing it into a metal basket with chains on it. UDG is a disc golf video game with a unique take on 'golf' style games. Featuring a character creator with real DG brands, explore-able courses. Come and play a round.
